text: emanaki yakhana payagambaragana nairasye patita haye yetena, emanaki erupa dharana karate suru karatena ye, tadera anumana bujhi mithyaya parinata ha'oyara upakrama hayechila, takhana tadera kache amara sahayya pauche. Atahpara ami yadera ceyechi tara ud'dhara peyeche. Amara sasti aparadhi sampradaya theke pratihata haya na.
